        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This intricately carved wooden staff is warm to the touch and thrums with inner energy. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify abjuration magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Shield]{Shield}</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Alarm]{Alarm}</em>, <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Feather Fall]{Feather Fall}</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Dispel Magic]{Dispel Magic}</em>, <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Endure Elements]{Endure Elements}</em>, <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Resist Energy]{Resist Energy}</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Alarm]{Alarm}</em>, <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Glyph of Warding]{Glyph of Warding}</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Dimensional Anchor]{Dimensional Anchor}</em>, <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Dispel Magic]{Dispel Magic}</em>, <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Resist Energy]{Resist Energy}</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
